Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, do whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I like Koizumi or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I know how to perform magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use my magic to bring you happiness, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I'm the one Koizumi-san likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd fall for someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For real this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop liking Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we really can go back to the way we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:13.81,Title,,0,0,0,,The Fist of Love!\NAccept it, a Maiden's Spirit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D'ya see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna lose to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge me any time you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani really is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you meant to be cheering for Maity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Maity-sama is wonderful, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Otani tries so hard despite being so short...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He deserves some praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's going on with you and Otani anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We've progressed so little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...that we've gone back to the way we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The comedy duo has been revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Revived"? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly did you guys end up like that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. This is the most comfortable way for us to be anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, are you aware of your situation right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,President Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,Maity Love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Maity club is... is disbanded now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so awful that Maity-sensei has a fiancée!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to hide it or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I guess someone told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is really down about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't got you down, has it, Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no... uh... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity, get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa says she and Otani-kun are back to being a comedy duo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"What" nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite what people might think, you're actually quite timid, aren't you, Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case, I'm glad that Otani-kun is better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic spell hasn't broken yet, Koizumi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather 'round! Gather 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His ankle has healed, so he's in top form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And since his final basketball competition is coming up, he's trying even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I'm the one Koizumi-san likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd fall for someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...he was jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to hold on to any inappropriate hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna go back to the way it was. Back to the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...what are you going to do from here on in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm ever so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are just sooo long...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, are you really fine with things going back to the way they were before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So the basketball competition is going to be this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I might come watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be bored, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'll bring that with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... the kind of cute things that a manager would bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemons in soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth would that taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, lemons in vinegar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How sour would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But I want to cheer you on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I eat anything weird like that, I'll be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make it for Maity-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. The coach will be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't need that guy any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be he really is jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, shaking your head like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww... That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please dip the lemons in honey, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's it. Honey, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the way it was,\Nback to the way it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey-dipped lemons, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bittersweet, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! Forget reviving the comedy duo... Just hurry up and get together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If only Otani would make a move now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end I guess it's Otani-kun who holds the key to all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, why don't you give him a push?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Let's just leave the youngsters to their own devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave these two alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...they'll go on like that until they're old and gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Too true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Push him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Push him down and claim him as your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It annoys me just watching you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to get together, hurry up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier said than done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I've decided I'm not going to hold on to any hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you haven't given up, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.15,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Bullseye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're just going to wait like that until Otani confesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for that guy to take the initiative is like going fishing in a swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But there might be koi swimming in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of pool are you thinking of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? You seem to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find out the tournament draw tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, for basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's our last big competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, come shopping with me after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if we fluke it to the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go for it, I really go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be held responsible if you fall for me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a joke, a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, at the end of the day, I just can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it... is it so bad if I hold on to just a little bit of hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is... the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a little too energetic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My darling is just a bench warmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still going to cheer for them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're going to come and watch us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakao-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The competition draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Lemme see, lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, since we're all going, let's invite Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...and cheer them on properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, our first opponents are last year's champions. They're real veterans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going for the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. He's turned into a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.31,Overlap,,0,0,0,,His spirit left his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite what people may think, you're actually quite timid, aren't you, Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As Maity said, I'm just afraid to find out what Otani is really thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please dip the lemons in honey, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just go back to pretending things are the way they were before,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...without doing anything,\N I'll definitely regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what Otani thinks of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Risa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The match is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?! Don't scare me so early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was up all night making our cheering gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheering gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:11.90,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani for Life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,OTANI CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.70,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani for Life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, you're all part of the Otani Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so down. Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cheer for you from the bench, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you Captain Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey man, we're your first opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I... My... Me... My... You... You are... H-Huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! We're the Otani Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We met our opponents just now, and it left him quite shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He wandered off somewhere in a daze.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the first match about to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry. I'll go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. I got dragged into the Otani Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. I'm just a bench warmer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer for Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Nakao-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say I'm trying to focus my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Otani Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, now. The match is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this Otani Club?\NHow embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you men, embarrassing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After I came specifically to cheer you on and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. You don't need to cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're going to lose anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more embarrassing if you're cheering away loudly while we're losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You slacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep saying you'll lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...you won't be able to win even if you do have a chance, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what can I do against those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to cheer for a guy like you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call you a loser midget for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed up all night, so I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! After making a girl with a boyfriend act so disloyally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm wearing one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to watch a pointless match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That... That useless loser midget...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's a loser midget?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you go home after you've cheered me on properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cheering for someone with no spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. I'm fired up and ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've received it, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That Idiot Punch of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely. You'll fall for me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you want, say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no normal height range...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Will they be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When Otani goes for it, he really goes for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He got past that tall guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,DO YOUR BEST\NOTANI
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did you put on these lemons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ri"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any honey, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I didn't eat these before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I stayed up all night, rubbing sleepy eyes in order to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you came to cheer me on and all, but we still lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you were still really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You made me fall for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I played so well thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you said you've given up on me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just... no good without you, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, that idiot! What is she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.06,0:23:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, what do you want for your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a cute ring or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is your love, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: The Best Birthday in History.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:20.04,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,The Best Birthday in History
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
